        "quoted": {
          "id": "2032176810327421038",
          "text": "I’m proud to be joining SpaceX and xAI with @milichab \n\nIt has become clear that software is changing fundamentally. More and more, people can shape the tools they use directly, and the ceiling of what can be built keeps rising.\n\nWhat makes xAI special is the scale of its ambition: to build from first principles all the way out to the stars.\n\nI’m especially grateful to work on products that expand human agency and freedom. That mission is deeply personal to me. My family came to the United States fleeing communism, and the belief that freedom should be part of the next generation of the internet has driven me every day since Andrew and I started Skiff. Now, we get to work on intelligence, understanding, and freedom on a universal scale.",
